data.label: Transaction Security Policy
data.query: SELECT DeveloperName,MasterLabel, EventName,BlockMessage FROM TransactionSecurityPolicy WHERE NamespacePrefix='' ORDER BY LastModifiedDate DESC LIMIT 20

data.label: Security Health Check Risks
data.query: SELECT Id,DurableId,RiskType,Setting,SettingGroup,OrgValue,OrgValueRaw,StandardValue,StandardValueRaw,SecurityHealthCheckId,SettingRiskCategory FROM SecurityHealthCheckRisks where RiskType!='MEETS_STANDARD'  LIMIT 20

data.label: Api Anomaly
data.query:
SELECT Score, UserId, EventDate, SecurityEventData, Summary
FROM ApiAnomalyEventStore

data.label: Security Settings
data.query: SELECT Id, FullName FROM SecuritySettings   LIMIT 20
